com.miura.sdk.ber

Enum TagDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TagDescriptor>
      • com.miura.sdk.ber.TagDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TagDescriptor>

    public enum TagDescriptor
extends java.lang.Enum<TagDescriptor>
    Collection of known EMV tags commonly used during EMV transaction processing. 
         See Annex A of "EMV v4.3 Book 3 Application Specification" for element definitions.
